{"lastModified":1771851073260,"uri":"c::8345304695::vessel::d5cccce0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLagoon 450 F Luxury “Metra” offered by Cata Sailing from our charter base in Trogir, is a perfect choice for a family, a couple with guests or a large group of friends. This yacht is stable when anchored. She offers wonderful visibility, space and great comfort. One of the best key features of this yacht is the raised flybridge. It gives great visibility and acts as the main cockpit. A  natural lighting and ventilation flow to all areas is perfectly designed. Therefore you hardly notice whether you are inside or outside. She is a spacious, well-appointed sailing catamaran with a charter-friendly layout and loads of deck area for relaxing during your charter.\n\nLagoon 450 F Luxury “Metra” boasts 4 en suite double cabins, ideal for up to eight guests in total. Light and airy, with sea views, each cabin is equipped with AC for absolute comfort. For the active charter guest, the tender and water toys are a 3,5 m tender with a 20HP  engine and other toys such as a Standup paddle and Snorkeling gear. Metra offers the perfect setting for the ultimate family getaway- space, privacy, luxury and comfort at affordable prices. If you’re interested in chartering this beauty send us a non-binding Booking request.","blueprint":{"name":"METRA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccce0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::15f25ea0-bc91-11ef-b6b7-5f88f4afeef2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccce0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::50d28e60-bc95-11ef-ab0c-05dc54da7c12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccce0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::50d5e9c0-bc95-11ef-ab0c-05dc54da7c12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccce0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::50d57490-bc95-11ef-ab0c-05dc54da7c12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc